# Inventory Item JSON Schema

Each “food item” in inventory is represented as an object conforming to this schema:

```jsonc
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "title": "InventoryItem",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ["id","name","category","quantity","expiryDate"],
  "properties": {
    "id": {
      "type": "string",
      "format": "uuid",
      "description": "Unique item identifier (UUID or SKU)."
    },
    "name": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Human-readable name, e.g. 'Organic Large Eggs (12)'."
    },
    "quantity": {
      "type": "integer",
      "minimum": 1,
      "description": "Number of units."
    },
    "unit": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Measurement unit (e.g. 'pcs','g','L')."
    },
    "expiryDate": {
      "type": "string",
      "format": "date-time",
      "description": "ISO 8601 expiry date (e.g. '2025-06-19T00:00:00Z')."
    },
    "purchaseDate": {
      "type": "string",
      "format": "date-time",
      "description": "ISO 8601 purchase date."
    },
    "cost": {
      "type": "number",
      "minimum": 0,
      "description": "Cost paid, for analytics (e.g. 2.99)."
    },
    "allergens": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": { "type": "string" },
      "description": "List of allergen keywords (e.g. 'eggs','gluten')."
    },
    "dietaryTags": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "string",
        "enum": ["vegetarian","vegan","gluten-free","dairy-free","nut-free"]
      },
      "description": "Dietary suitability tags."
    },
  }
}

